output.dependency: The values in the column representing surgical infection prevention codes have a direct dependency on the descriptions of these codes, which summarize the relevant procedures or outcomes associated with each code.
The values in the column representing heart attack codes have a direct dependency on the descriptions, which explain the particular treatment or intervention for heart attack patients for each code.
The values in the column representing heart failure codes depend directly on the descriptions that detail the interventions or treatments for heart failure patients as specified by each code.
The pneumonia codes in this column also rely directly on the corresponding descriptions that detail the treatment protocols or outcomes specific to pneumonia patients.
